相规划细则，现分解为县级执行单元：
- 县令一：数据采集 - 获取X公司FY2024 10-K
- 县令二：数据提取 - COGS与存货数值
- 县令三：计算执行 - 周转率核算
- 县令四：校验确认 - 结果验证

风险已识别：文件获取延迟、数据口径一致性
</summary>



```json
{
  "decision": "next",
  "summary": "[调度中] US Steel FY2024存货周转率核算派发方案已制定，4县任务已派发",
  "updates": {
    "dispatch_plan": [
      {
        "county": "xian_data_collection",
        "task": "获取United States Steel Corporation (NYSE:X) FY2024年度10-K年报文件",
        "deliverable": "10-K文件或 SEC filings页面",
        "deadline": "T+0.5",
        "tool": "web_search + web_fetch"
      },
      {
        "county": "xian_data_extraction",
        "task": "从10-K中提取FY2024的Cost of Goods Sold (COGS)和Inventory存货数值",
        "deliverable": "COGS数值、期初存货、期末存货",
        "deadline": "T+1",
        "dependencies": ["xian_data_collection"]
      },
      {
        "county": "xian_calculation",
        "task": "计算存货周转率 = COGS / 平均存货（期初+期末）/2",
        "deliverable": "存货周转率数值",
        "deadline": "T+1.5",
        "dependencies": ["xian_data_extraction"]
      },
      {
        "county": "xian_verification",
        "task": "校验计算结果，核对公式与数据口径一致性",
        "deliverable": "校验报告",
        "deadline": "T+2",
        "dependencies": ["xian_calculation"]
      }
    ],
    "risks": [
      {
        "risk_id": "R1",
        "description": "10-K文件获取可能因SEC网站访问延迟",
        "impact": "阻塞数据提取阶段"
      },
      {
        "risk_id": "R2",
        "description": "COGS与存货统计口径可能存在不一致",
        "impact": "计算结果偏差"
      },
      {
        "risk_id": "R3",
        "description": "FY2024财年截止日期需确认(12/31/2024或12/31/2023)",
        "impact": "数据提取准确性"
      }
    ],
    "mitigation": [
      {
        "risk_id": "R1",
        "mitigation": "准备备用搜索关键词：'US Steel 2024 10-K annual report SEC filing'"
      },
      {
        "risk_id": "R2",
        "mitigation": "确认COGS来自Consolidated Statements of Operations，存货来自Balance Sheet"
      },
      {
        "risk_id": "R3",
        "mitigation": "US Steel财年为日历年，确认使用FY2024 (Year ended December 31, 2024)"
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

